  "texts": [
    "The approach we used has the advantage of being straightforward to implement across a large feature set without expert clinical knowledge.",
    "If a similar process was put into real-world use, there would be the option to allow clinicians to set the thresholds for binning rather than relying on the population minimum and maximum.",
    "This could potentially help reduce the",
